OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774537862
OL,3,CFM accuses Farage of insulting Wales
OL,4,Cin 'foreign speakers' video
OL,6,FThe First Minister has accused Nigel
OL,7,FFarage of insulting Wales by
OL,8,Fdescribing Welsh people as "foreign
OL,9,Fspeakers" in a video.
OL,11,FSpeaking at First Minister's Questions
OL,12,Fon Tuesday, Baroness Eluned Morgan
OL,13,Fsaid the comments proved the Reform UK
OL,14,Fleader has "no understanding" of life
OL,15,Fin Wales.
OL,17,FMr Farage made the remarks in a clip
OL,18,Fhe was paid to make on Cameo, a
OL,19,Fpersonalised video platform, to
OL,20,Fcelebrate a wedding, the Guardian
OL,21,Freported last week.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@IO]vD@LOUvD@]O]
