OL,3,CFM accuses Farage of insulting Wales
OL,4,Cin 'foreign speakers' video
OL,6,FIn the video, Mr Farage said: "Gutted
OL,7,FI couldn't attend the wedding, I
OL,8,Fwanted to come, but I heard that half
OL,9,Fthe guests were Welsh and, I don't
OL,10,Fknow.
OL,12,F"Who knows what would have happened
OL,13,Fwith all those foreign speakers there?
OL,14,FI don't know."
OL,26,@nD@_OUtD@AOUvD@NO]
