CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774537862
OL,3,CFM accuses Farage of insulting Wales
OL,4,Cin 'foreign speakers' video
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Darren Millar, the leader
OL,7,Fof the Welsh Conservatives in the
OL,8,FSenedd, said: "Do you agree that the
OL,9,Fclip by Nigel Farage last week, that
OL,10,Fdescribed the Welsh language as a
OL,11,Fforeign language, is an insult to the
OL,12,Fpeople of Wales and it's clear that
OL,13,FNigel Farage doesn't care about Wales
OL,14,Fat all?
OL,16,F"And that this clip demonstrates that
OL,17,FNigel Farage is ready to say anything
OL,18,Ffor money?"
OL,26,@pD@OOUxD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
