PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774537862
OL,3,CFM accuses Farage of insulting Wales
OL,4,Cin 'foreign speakers' video
OL,6,FLady Morgan said: "I do agree with
OL,7,Fyou, I do think that it was an insult
OL,8,Fto the language and to our nation in
OL,9,Fterms of the way that Nigel Farage
OL,10,Fspoke of our language.
OL,12,F"The fact is that he will do anything
OL,13,Ffor money, anything at all.
OL,15,F"We must also bear in mind that he has
OL,16,Fno understanding whatsoever of how we
OL,17,Flive here in Wales."
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOUwD@AOUyD@TO]
